fields.day1_exercises:
Main Workout:
Squats – 4x8
Incline Dumbbell Press – 4x10
Bent-over Rows – 3x10
Plank-to-Push-ups – 3x12

HIIT Finisher (3 rounds):
20 sec Sprint
40 sec Rest
fields.day2_exercises:
Main Workout:
Deadlifts – 3x8
Pull-ups (Weighted if possible) – 3x8
Lunges – 3x10/leg
Russian Twists (Weighted) – 3x20

Cardio:
25 min incline treadmill walk
fields.day3_exercises:
Main Workout:
Box Jumps – 3x12
Kettlebell Swings – 3x15
Burpees – 3x10
Jump Rope – 3x2 min

HIIT Finisher (4 rounds):
30 sec High Knees
30 sec Jump Squats
fields.notes:
Best For: Those with a solid foundation who want efficient fat-burning workouts.
Progressive overload: Increase intensity gradually.
Focus on form and explosive movements.
Maintain a caloric deficit for optimal fat loss.
